name: HOOVABIKE HB ForgPP 033
description:
HB FrogPP 033 was a whip used by King Geli and then reworked by Alpha Geli for space travel. HB FrogPP contains a navigational system, auto-calculation software that can determine Myneral.

With 4.4m long / 3.15m wide, weighing 12 tons. This Hoovabike suits an endurable mission. Although it's reworked, the main technical aspects and primary function are still the same as the royal hoovabike.

Manufactured in year 3, Geli Exo Planet.
